<inglise> 4. </inglise>
<eesti> 4. </eesti>
<inglise> At the request of a Member State or, under the arrangements laid down in paragraph 3, of the Commission, the Member States shall consult each other, where appropriate within the Fund Committee or any other competent body, for the purpose of closing any gaps which become apparent in the course of application of provisions in force and which prejudice Community interests. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui kehtivate &otilde;igusaktide kohaldamisel ilmneb &uuml;henduse huve kahjustavaid puudusi, annavad liikmesriigid ja komisjon liikmesriigi taotluse korral v&otilde;i l&otilde;ikes 3 s&auml;testatud korra kohaselt komisjoni taotluse korral &uuml;ksteisele n&otilde;u nende puuduste k&otilde;rvaldamiseks, vajaduse korral fondi komitee v&otilde;i muu p&auml;deva asutuse kaudu. </eesti>
