<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The information referred to in paragraph 1 may not, in particular, be sent to persons other than those in the Member States or within the Community institutions whose duties require that they have access to it, unless the Member State supplying it has expressly agreed. </inglise>
